WEBVTT

00:10:27.571 --> 00:10:31.100
dok mu ljubav spava,
bezbedno, u zagrljaju.

00:10:31.735 --> 00:10:34.340
Stići do ovog mesta,

00:10:34.364 --> 00:10:36.455
proživeti do ovog trena:

00:10:36.479 --> 00:10:38.594
bezmerne lakoće.

00:10:39.392 --> 00:10:42.313
Gustina tame počinje da magli braonkasto.

00:10:42.789 --> 00:10:45.767
Privremeni, jarkocrveni kolorit,

00:10:45.791 --> 00:10:47.802
a potom tugaljiva golubija elegija.

00:10:48.390 --> 00:10:50.780
Samurovina bledi ka sivoj;

00:10:50.804 --> 00:10:53.972
predmeti izranjaju, vukući senke;

00:10:53.996 --> 00:10:55.971
noć stari ka danu.

00:10:56.540 --> 00:10:58.006
Grad se komeša.

00:10:58.958 --> 00:11:02.858
Biće još zora, noći, bleštavih podneva.